丹中尉总是有些奇怪的感觉
Lieutenant Dan was always getting these funny feelings

753
00:45:05,330 --> 00:45:08,424
对于路上的风吹草动
about a rock or a trail or the road,

754
00:45:08,500 --> 00:45:11,435
他会叫我们蹲下 安静
so he'd tell us to get down, shut up.

755
00:45:11,503 --> 00:45:12,595
蹲下！
Get down!

756
00:45:12,670 --> 00:45:13,762
安静！
Shut up!

757
00:45:14,839 --> 00:45:16,101
我们都照做
So we did.

758
00:45:32,624 --> 00:45:35,889
我对什么都不太明白
Now I don't know much about anything,

759
00:45:35,960 --> 00:45:38,895
但我想美国最好的年青人
but I think some of America's best young men

760
00:45:38,963 --> 00:45:40,225
都参加了这场战争
served in this war.

761
00:45:40,298 --> 00:45:42,562
那是非尼克斯来的达拉斯
There was Dallas from Phoenix.

762
00:45:43,968 --> 00:45:46,732
克利夫兰…他来自底特律
Cleveland... he was from Detroit.

763
00:45:46,804 --> 00:45:48,032
嘿 泰克斯
Hey, Tex.

764
00:45:48,106 --> 00:45:49,596
嘿 泰克斯
Hey, Tex.

765
00:45:49,674 --> 00:45:51,266
究竟出什么事了？
What the hell's going on?

766
00:45:51,342 --> 00:45:53,537
泰克斯是…
And Tex was...

767
00:45:53,611 --> 00:45:56,205
嗯 我不记得泰克斯是哪里人了
Well, I don't remember where Tex come from...

768
00:45:56,281 --> 00:45:57,805
啊 没事了
Ah, nothing.

769
00:46:01,719 --> 00:46:03,744
第四排 站起来
Fourth platoon, on your feet.

770
00:46:03,821 --> 00:46:06,722
你们10分钟内赶到河边
Y'all got 10 clicks to go to that river.

771
00:46:06,791 --> 00:46:08,383
出发
Move out.

772
00:46:08,459 --> 00:46:10,893
一二一！
1, 2! Hup!

773
00:46:12,297 --> 00:46:13,730
齐步走！
Step it up!

774
00:46:13,798 --> 00:46:15,129
那边好像不错
Look alive out there .

775
00:46:15,200 --> 00:46:16,633
在越南最好的一点
The good thing about Vietnam

776
00:46:16,701 --> 00:46:18,965
就是总有地方可去
is there was always someplace to go.

777
00:46:19,037 --> 00:46:20,299
小心手雷！
Fire in the hole!

778
00:46:23,875 --> 00:46:26,469
阿甘 搜一下那个洞
Gump, check out that hole.

779
00:46:26,544 --> 00:46:29,479
也总有事情可做
And there was always something to do.

780
00:46:29,547 --> 00:46:30,639
准备好！
Mount'em up!

781
00:46:30,715 --> 00:46:32,512
散开！掩护他！
Spread out! Cover his back!

782
00:46:37,589 --> 00:46:40,183
有一天开始下雨了
One day it started raining,

783
00:46:40,258 --> 00:46:43,591
然后一直不停的下了四个月
and it didn't quit for four months.

784
00:46:43,661 --> 00:46:47,097
我们经历了各种各样的雨…
We've been through every kind of rain there is...

785
00:46:47,165 --> 00:46:49,793
象小针样的雨
little bitty stinging rain

786
00:46:50,315 --> 00:46:53,524
还有倾盆大雨
and big old fat rain,

787
00:46:53,585 --> 00:46:56,027
从侧面下的雨
rain that flew in side ways,

788
00:46:56,145 --> 00:46:57,806
有时甚至还有
and sometimes rain even seemed

789
00:46:57,883 --> 00:47:01,215
从下往上的雨
to come straight up from underneath.

790
00:47:01,287 --> 00:47:04,813
连晚上也下雨
Shoot, it even rained at night.

791
00:47:04,892 --> 00:47:06,652
嘿 福雷斯
Hey, Forrest.

792
00:47:06,727 --> 00:47:07,815
嘿 布巴
Hey, Bubba.

793
00:47:07,897 --> 00:47:10,159
我的背靠着你的背
I'm going to lean up against you.

794
00:47:10,233 --> 00:47:11,663
你的背靠着你的背
You lean up against me.

795
00:47:11,735 --> 00:47:13,997
这样我们睡着的时候
This way we don't have to sleep

796
00:47:14,073 --> 00:47:16,003
头就不会钻进泥里
with our heads in the mud.

797
00:47:16,075 --> 00:47:18,667
你知道为何我们是好伙伴 福雷斯？
You know why we're a good partnership, Forrest?

798
00:47:18,747 --> 00:47:22,010
因为我们互相照顾
'Cause we be watching out for one another,

799
00:47:22,085 --> 00:47:23,845
就像兄弟一样
like brothers and stuff.

800
00:47:25,757 --> 00:47:27,347
嘿 福雷斯
Hey, Forrest,

801
00:47:27,427 --> 00:47:29,517
我在考虑一件事
something I been thinking about.

802
00:47:29,596 --> 00:47:32,528
我有个很重要的问题要问你
I got a very important question to ask you.

803
00:47:34,269 --> 00:47:36,199
你想不想
How would you like to go

804
00:47:36,272 --> 00:47:38,202
和我一起去捕虾？
into the shrimping business with me?

805
00:47:39,778 --> 00:47:41,038
好的
O.K.

806
00:47:41,113 --> 00:47:42,873
兄弟 你听我说
Man, I tell you what.

807
00:47:42,950 --> 00:47:45,212
我全计划好了
I got it all figured out, too.

808
00:47:45,287 --> 00:47:46,717
我们捕到的虾多少磅
So many pounds of shrimp

809
00:47:46,789 --> 00:47:48,219
拿来付买船的贷款
will pay off the boat.

810
00:47:48,291 --> 00:47:49,721
多少磅拿来付油费
So many pounds for gas.

811
00:47:49,792 --> 00:47:51,722
我们住在船上就行
We'll live right on the boat.

812
00:47:51,796 --> 00:47:54,058
这样就不用付房租
We ain't got to pay no rent.

813
00:47:54,133 --> 00:47:56,063
我们合伙来干
We can just work it together,

814
00:47:56,136 --> 00:47:58,066
全部都对半分
split everything right down the middle.

815
00:47:58,139 --> 00:48:00,229
兄弟 告诉你 五五分成
Man, I'm telling you, 50-50.

816
00:48:00,309 --> 00:48:03,333
还有 福雷斯 虾可以随便吃
Hey, Forrest, all the shrimp you can eat.

817
00:48:04,914 --> 00:48:07,506
真是个好主意
That's a fine idea.

818
00:48:07,586 --> 00:48:10,347
布巴的主意真得很好
Bubba did have a fine idea.

819
00:48:14,900 --> 00:48:15,600
我甚至写信给珍妮
I even wrote Jenny

820
00:48:16,235 --> 00:48:18,165
告诉她这件事情
and told her all about it.

821
00:48:18,238 --> 00:48:19,828
我给她寄信…
I sent her letters...

822
00:48:19,908 --> 00:48:21,998
差不多每天都寄
Not every day, but almost.

823
00:48:22,077 --> 00:48:24,339
告诉她我在做的事
I told her what I was doing

824
00:48:24,414 --> 00:48:26,847
也问她在做些什么
and asked her what she was doing

825
00:48:26,918 --> 00:48:30,110
告诉她我经常想念她
and told her how I thought about her always.

826
00:48:31,482 --> 00:48:33,412
和我多么希望
And how I was looking forward

827
00:48:33,485 --> 00:48:35,415
能收到她一封回信
to getting a letter from her

828
00:48:35,488 --> 00:48:38,249
只要她有时间
just as soon as she had the time.

829
00:48:38,327 --> 00:48:41,259
我总是告诉她我很平安
I'd always let her know that I was O. K.

830
00:48:41,330 --> 00:48:48,760
然后我的落款总是“爱你的福雷斯甘”
Then I'd sign each letter "Love, Forrest Gump. "

831
00:48:58,688 --> 00:49:01,449
“有事情正在发生”
# There's somethin' happenin' here #

832
00:49:02,795 --> 00:49:06,389
那一天 我们象平常一样走着
This one day, we was out walking like always,

833
00:49:06,466 --> 00:49:10,230
然后 忽然之间
and then, just like that,

834
00:49:10,306 --> 00:49:12,236
就像有人关掉天上的水龙头
somebody turned off the rain,

835
00:49:12,309 --> 00:49:13,899
太阳出来了
and the sun come out.

836
00:49:13,978 --> 00:49:16,739
“我必须小心”
# I got to beware #

837
00:49:16,816 --> 00:49:18,906
有埋伏！
Ambush!

838
00:49:18,985 --> 00:49:20,915
快找掩护！
Take cover!

839
00:49:29,503 --> 00:49:32,129
快把它拿过来 见鬼
Get that pig up here, god damn it!

840
00:49:32,265 --> 00:49:34,390
福雷斯 你没事吧？
Forrest! You okay?

841
00:49:37,005 --> 00:49:39,903
强手 强手！
Strong-arm, Strong-arm!

842
00:49:39,976 --> 00:49:42,771
嘿！有个人倒下了！
Hey! We got a man down!

843
00:49:42,847 --> 00:49:46,304
强手 我们是第雷利六号！完毕！
Strong-arm, this is Leg Lima 6! Over!

844
00:49:46,385 --> 00:49:48,818
收到 强手！我们遭到袭击
Roger, Strong-arm! Be advised we have incoming

845
00:49:48,890 --> 00:49:51,289
在蓝点树林
from the tree line at point blue

846
00:49:51,360 --> 00:49:53,690
从两个方向！有冲锋枪和火箭筒！
plus two! A.K.s and rockets!

847
00:49:53,764 --> 00:49:55,024
我们损失惨重！
We're getting it hard!

848
00:49:55,098 --> 00:49:56,654
哑火！哑火！
Misfire! Misfire!

849
00:49:57,735 --> 00:49:59,530
见鬼！
God damn it!

850
00:50:01,108 --> 00:50:05,041
把那玩意扔掉撤退到树林！
Get that pig unfucked and on the treeline!

851
00:50:06,882 --> 00:50:09,474
他们压住我们了
They got us, and it hurt.

852
00:50:09,554 --> 00:50:13,045
我们准备撤退
We're going to move back to the blue line.

853
00:50:13,126 --> 00:50:16,024
撤退！撤退！
Pull back! Pull back!

854
00:50:16,097 --> 00:50:18,084
福雷斯！跑 福雷斯！
Forrest! Run, Forrest!

855
00:50:18,166 --> 00:50:19,892
撤退！
Pull back!

856
00:50:19,969 --> 00:50:22,162
跑！跑 兄弟！
Run! Run, man!

857
00:50:22,240 --> 00:50:23,328
跑！
Run!

858
00:50:23,408 --> 00:50:24,668
撤退 阿甘！
Pull back, Gump!

859
00:50:26,245 --> 00:50:29,405
跑 见鬼！跑！
Run, God damn it! Run!

860
00:50:55,355 --> 00:50:59,380
我一直跑 就像珍妮要我做的
I ran and ran just like Jenny told me to.

861
00:51:02,132 --> 00:51:04,325
我跑得这么快这么远
I ran so far so fast

862
00:51:04,401 --> 00:51:06,834
很快就只剩下我一个人
that pretty soon I was all by myself,

863
00:51:06,905 --> 00:51:08,495
这下糟糕了
which was a bad thing.

864
00:51:08,575 --> 00:51:09,663
布巴
Bubba.

865
00:51:12,246 --> 00:51:14,336
布巴是我最好的朋友
Bubba was my best good friend.

866
00:51:14,417 --> 00:51:16,850
我要保证他没事
I had to make sure he was O.K.

867
00:51:25,935 --> 00:51:28,368
你在哪儿？
Where the hell are you?

868
00:51:28,437 --> 00:51:30,527
布巴！
Bubba!

869
00:51:30,608 --> 00:51:33,540
我回去找布巴途中
And on my way back to find Bubba,

870
00:51:33,613 --> 00:51:36,374
发现有个人躺在地上
well, there was this boy laying on the ground.

871
00:51:36,451 --> 00:51:37,435
泰克斯
Tex.

872
00:51:39,387 --> 00:51:40,977
好了
O.K.

873
00:51:41,056 --> 00:51:43,489
我不能让他单独躺在那里
I couldn't let him lay there all alone,

874
00:51:43,561 --> 00:51:44,991
他非常害怕
scared the way he was,

875
00:51:45,063 --> 00:51:46,823
所以我扶起他
so I grabbed him up

876
00:51:46,899 --> 00:51:48,625
背他逃出那里
and run him out of there.

877
00:52:03,856 --> 00:52:06,584
每次我回去找布巴
Every time I went back looking for Bubba,

878
00:52:06,661 --> 00:52:08,091
总有人在喊：
somebody else was saying,

879
00:52:08,162 --> 00:52:11,094
“救命 福雷斯 救命！”
"Help me, Forrest, help me! "

880
00:52:17,678 --> 00:52:19,837
好了 好了
O.K. Here. Here .

881
00:52:22,152 --> 00:52:25,118
不要怕 兄弟 躺下 你会没事的
No sweat, man. Lay back. You'll be O.K.

882
00:52:27,526 --> 00:52:31,986
我开始担心我可能永远找不到布巴
I started to get scared that I might never find Bubba.

883
00:52:32,067 --> 00:52:33,497
我知道我的处境
I know my position

884
00:52:33,568 --> 00:52:35,465
越来越危险！
is danger close!

885
00:52:35,538 --> 00:52:37,971
这一带到处都是“越共”
We got Charlie all over this area.

886
00:52:38,043 --> 00:52:40,975
我这儿需要快速的支援 完毕
I got to have those fast movers in here now. Over.

887
00:52:41,047 --> 00:52:43,480
丹中尉 科曼死了！
Lieutenant Dan, Coleman's dead!

888
00:52:43,551 --> 00:52:44,981
我知道他死了！
I know he's dead!

889
00:52:45,053 --> 00:52:47,985
我他妈的整个排全完了！
My whole goddamn platoon is wiped out!

890
00:52:48,058 --> 00:52:49,488
该死的！
God damn it!

891
00:52:49,559 --> 00:52:51,489
你干什么？
What are you doing?

892
00:52:51,562 --> 00:52:52,992
你把我放下！
You leave me here!

893
00:52:53,064 --> 00:52:54,994
走开 把我留在这里！
Get away . Just leave me here!

894
00:52:55,067 --> 00:52:56,497
走开！
Get out!

895
00:52:56,570 --> 00:53:00,503
啊！我说把我留在这儿 该死的！
Aah! God, I said leave me here, God damn it!

896
00:53:00,575 --> 00:53:02,939
雷利 我是强手
Leg Lima, this is Strong-arm.

897
00:53:03,013 --> 00:53:05,979
我们马上提供快速支援 完毕
Be advised your fast movers are in bound. Over.

898
00:53:06,050 --> 00:53:09,450
突然好像有什么东西跳起来咬我
Then it felt like something just jumped up and bit me.

899
00:53:09,522 --> 00:53:12,283
啊！什么东西在咬我！
Aah! Something bit me!

900
00:53:19,203 --> 00:53:21,133
你这狗娘养的！
You son of a bitch!

901
00:53:22,609 --> 00:53:25,633
我不能离开我的排
I can't leave the platoon.

902
00:53:25,712 --> 00:53:27,644
我叫你把我留在那里 阿甘
I told you to leave me there, Gump.

903
00:53:27,800 --> 00:53:30,682
丢下我 你自己逃吧！
Forget about me. Get your self out!

904
00:53:30,755 --> 00:53:32,984
你听到我的话没有？
Did you hear what I said?

905
00:53:33,057 --> 00:53:35,490
阿甘 见鬼 放下我
Gump, damn it, put me down.

906
00:53:35,561 --> 00:53:38,084
你自己逃吧
Get your ass out of here.

907
00:53:40,069 --> 00:53:43,194
我没叫你救我出去 去你妈的！
I didn't ask you to pull me out of there, God damn you!

908
00:53:43,274 --> 00:53:45,000
你又要去哪里？
Where the hell do you think you're going?

909
00:53:45,100 --> 00:53:46,708
去找布巴
To get Bubba.

910
00:53:46,820 --> 00:53:49,713
我已经呼叫空袭了
I got an air strike in bound right now.

911
00:53:49,784 --> 00:53:52,274
他们会把那里炸平
They're going to nape the whole area.

912
00:53:52,355 --> 00:53:53,500
留在这里！这是命令
Stay here! That's an order.

913
00:53:53,502 --> 00:53:56,321
我要找到布巴！
I gotta find Bubba!

914
00:54:11,548 --> 00:54:13,240
福雷斯
Forrest.

915
00:54:20,562 --> 00:54:21,891
布巴
Bubba.

916
00:54:21,965 --> 00:54:23,793
我没事 福雷斯
I'm O.K., Forrest.

917
00:54:23,867 --> 00:54:25,389
我没事
I'm O.K.

918
00:54:33,815 --> 00:54:35,836
啊 布巴 不
O-Oh, Bubba, no.

919
00:54:35,919 --> 00:54:37,714
我没事的
I'll be all right.

920
00:54:46,100 --> 00:54:47,188
行了
Come on.

921
00:54:47,269 --> 00:54:48,995
行了 行了
Come on. Come on.

922
00:54:52,977 --> 00:54:55,671
我没事 福雷斯
Ugh. I'm O.K., Forrest.

923
00:54:58,620 --> 00:55:00,550
我没事 我很好
I'm O.K. I'm fine.

924
00:55:37,077 --> 00:55:40,101
炸平那里
Top smoke. Get it up there .

925
00:55:40,182 --> 00:55:43,046
如果我知道这将是
If I'd have known this was going to be

926
00:55:43,118 --> 00:55:46,050
我和布巴的最后一次谈话
the last time me and Bubba was gonna talk,

927
00:55:46,123 --> 00:55:49,055
我会想些更好的话来说
I'd of thought of something better to say.

928
00:55:49,129 --> 00:55:50,182
嘿 布巴
Hey, Bubba.

929
00:55:50,263 --> 00:55:51,523
嘿 福雷斯
Hey, Forrest.

930
00:55:53,968 --> 00:55:55,398
福雷斯…
Forrest...

931
00:55:55,472 --> 00:55:58,563
出什么事了？
Why did this happen?

932
00:55:58,643 --> 00:56:01,575
你中弹了
You got shot.

933
00:56:01,645 --> 00:56:06,014
布巴说了一句我永远不会忘记的话
Then Bubba said something I won't ever forget.

934
00:56:06,086 --> 00:56:09,646
我想回家
I want to go home.

935
00:56:09,726 --> 00:56:12,521
布巴是我最好的好朋友
Bubba was my best good friend.

936
00:56:12,596 --> 00:56:14,526
我还知道
And even I know

937
00:56:14,599 --> 00:56:18,034
好朋友不是那么容易找到的
that ain't something you can find just around the corner.

938
00:56:18,105 --> 00:56:21,540
布巴想当一个捕虾船的船长
Bubba was going to be a shrimping boat captain,

939
00:56:21,611 --> 00:56:25,910
但是 他却死在越南的一条河边
but instead, he died right there by that river in Vietnam.

940
00:56:31,492 --> 00:56:33,822
我要说的就是这些了
That's all I have to say about that.

941
00:56:36,033 --> 00:56:38,226
那是粒子弹 是吗？
It was a bullet, wasn't it?

942
00:56:40,139 --> 00:56:41,569
子弹？
