# Get down tonight... #

1503
01:29:37,125 --> 01:29:39,518
我没听到珍妮的消息
Now, I hadn't heard from Jenny

1504
01:29:39,590 --> 01:29:40,882
已经很久了
in a long while,

1505
01:29:40,957 --> 01:29:43,384
但我仍经常想念她
but I thought about her a lot.

1506
01:29:43,457 --> 01:29:46,544
不管她在做什么 我希望她开心
I hoped whatever she was doing made her happy.

1507
01:29:46,623 --> 01:29:51,641
“你不能改变那只小鸟”
# Oh, and the bird you cannot change #

1508
01:29:55,084 --> 01:30:01,771
“你不能改变这只小鸟”
# And this bird you cannot change #

1509
01:30:01,848 --> 01:30:09,217
“上天知道我无法改变”
# Lord knows I can't change #

1510
01:30:09,289 --> 01:30:16,220
“上天保佑我无法改变”
# Lord, help me, I can't change #

1511
01:31:32,438 --> 01:31:35,874
我时刻想念着珍妮
I thought about Jenny all the time.

1512
01:32:25,424 --> 01:32:30,020
丹中尉 你来做什么？
Lieutenant Dan, what are you doing here?

1513
01:32:30,095 --> 01:32:33,462
嗯 我想到海中施展拳脚
Well, thought I'd try out my sea legs.

1514
01:32:33,533 --> 01:32:36,468
可是你没有脚了 丹中尉
Well, you ain't got no legs, Lieutenant Dan.

1515
01:32:36,536 --> 01:32:37,969
是的 我知道
Yes, I know that.

1516
01:32:38,038 --> 01:32:42,236
你写了封信给我 白痴
You wrote me a letter, you idiot.

1517
01:32:42,309 --> 01:32:44,675
好了 福雷斯甘船长
Well, well. Captain Forrest Gump.

1518
01:32:44,746 --> 01:32:47,613
我要亲眼来看看…
I had to see this for myself...

1519
01:32:48,917 --> 01:32:50,384
并且…
and...

1520
01:32:50,453 --> 01:32:54,890
我说过如果你能当捕虾船的船长
I told you if you were ever a shrimp boat captain,

1521
01:32:54,957 --> 01:32:56,891
我就来当你的大副
that I'd be your first mate.

1522
01:32:56,960 --> 01:32:58,621
所以我来了
Well, here I am.

1523
01:32:58,695 --> 01:33:00,629
我是信守诺言的
I'm a man of my word .

1524
01:33:00,697 --> 01:33:01,721
好的
O.K.

1525
01:33:01,799 --> 01:33:03,960
但你别以为
But don't you be thinking

1526
01:33:04,035 --> 01:33:06,469
我会叫你长官
that I'm going to be calling you "sir."

1527
01:33:06,537 --> 01:33:07,469
不用 长官
No, sir.

1528
01:33:16,016 --> 01:33:17,540
这是我的船
It's my boat.

1529
01:33:20,721 --> 01:33:24,817
我觉得如果我们向东开
I have a feeling if we head due east,

1530
01:33:24,892 --> 01:33:28,453
我们就会找到虾 现在左转
we'll find some shrimp, so take a left.

1531
01:33:29,865 --> 01:33:31,298
向左转！
Take a left!

1532
01:33:31,366 --> 01:33:32,298
哪边？
Which way?

1533
01:33:32,368 --> 01:33:33,300
那边！
Over there!

1534
01:33:33,369 --> 01:33:34,802
他们在那边！
They're over there!

1535
01:33:34,871 --> 01:33:38,204
快打舵盘向左
Get on the wheel and take a left.

1536
01:33:38,275 --> 01:33:39,708
好的
O.K.

1537
01:33:41,045 --> 01:33:42,979
阿甘 你干什么？
Gump, what are you doing?

1538
01:33:43,047 --> 01:33:44,480
向左转！
Take a left!

1539
01:33:44,549 --> 01:33:45,538
左边！
Left!

1540
01:33:47,419 --> 01:33:51,355
那边我们会找到虾的 兄弟！
That's where we're going to find those shrimp, my boy!

1541
01:33:52,425 --> 01:33:54,552
那边我们会找到它们
That's where we'll find them.

1542
01:34:06,974 --> 01:34:08,908
还是没有虾 丹中尉
Still no shrimp, Lieutenant Dan.

1543
01:34:08,977 --> 01:34:10,911
好吧 我弄错了
O.K., so I was wrong.

1544
01:34:10,979 --> 01:34:13,914
嗯 我们怎么才能找到虾呢？
Well, how are we going to find them?

1545
01:34:13,983 --> 01:34:18,010
也许你可以去祷告
Maybe you should just pray for shrimp.

1546
01:34:18,088 --> 01:34:20,750
“所以我们祷告”
# So pray that #

1547
01:34:20,825 --> 01:34:24,090
“我在回家路上…”
# I'm homeward bound... #

1548
01:34:24,161 --> 01:34:26,857
所以我每个星期天都去教堂
So I went to church every Sunday.

1549
01:34:28,300 --> 01:34:30,234
有时丹中尉也来
Sometimes Lieutenant Dan came, too,

1550
01:34:30,302 --> 01:34:34,170
虽然他只让我负责祷告
though I think he left the praying up to me.

1551
01:34:48,690 --> 01:34:50,089
没有虾
No shrimp.

1552
01:34:51,193 --> 01:34:54,128
你那上帝到底在哪儿？
Where the hell's this God of yours?

1553
01:34:54,196 --> 01:34:56,630
奇怪的是丹中尉一说这话
It's funny Lieutenant Dan said that

1554
01:34:56,700 --> 01:35:00,517
上帝就来了
'cause right then God showed up.

1555
01:35:16,169 --> 01:35:18,603
你绝不能弄沉这条船！
You'll never sink this boat!

1556
01:35:18,671 --> 01:35:21,333
我当时很害怕
Now, me, I was scared,

1557
01:35:21,408 --> 01:35:25,469
但丹中尉 他像是发疯了
but Lieutenant Dan, he was mad.

1558
01:35:25,546 --> 01:35:26,535
来吧！
Come on!

1559
01:35:29,083 --> 01:35:31,381
你这算是风暴吗？
You call this a storm?

1560
01:35:31,453 --> 01:35:35,389
来吧 你这狗娘养的！
Come on, you son of a bitch!

1561
01:35:35,458 --> 01:35:39,394
咱们来较量一下吧！
It's time for a show down!

1562
01:35:39,463 --> 01:35:40,930
你和我！
You and me!

1563
01:35:40,997 --> 01:35:44,057
我就在这儿 来捉我吧！
I'm right here! Come and get me!

1564
01:35:46,737 --> 01:35:48,170
你绝不能弄沉…
You'll never sink...

1565
01:35:48,239 --> 01:35:49,536
这条…
this...

1566
01:35:49,607 --> 01:35:50,699
船！
boat!

1567
01:35:52,778 --> 01:35:54,873
卡门飓风昨天过境
Hurricane Carmen came through here yesterday,

1568
01:35:55,006 --> 01:35:56,803
沿途几乎摧毁了一切
destroying nearly everything in its path.

1569
01:35:56,876 --> 01:35:59,811
沿海的其他城镇也一样
And as in other towns up and down the coast,

1570
01:35:59,879 --> 01:36:02,677
拉巴特湾的捕虾业
Bayou La Batre's entire shrimping industry

1571
01:36:02,749 --> 01:36:05,081
成为卡门飓风的最大受害者
has fallen victim to Carmen

1572
01:36:05,152 --> 01:36:07,985
渔港完全成了废墟
and has been left in utter ruin.

1573
01:36:08,054 --> 01:36:09,487
记者被告知
This reporter has learned,

1574
01:36:09,557 --> 01:36:11,991
实际上只有一条捕虾船
in fact, only one shrimping boat

1575
01:36:12,059 --> 01:36:13,583
幸免于难
actually survived the storm.

1576
01:36:13,661 --> 01:36:16,129
露西 露西 福雷斯来了
Louise. Louise, there's Forrest.

1577
01:36:16,198 --> 01:36:19,292
从此以后 捕虾就很容易了
After that, shrimping was easy.

1578
01:36:19,368 --> 01:36:22,132
“将会有丰厚的回报”
# There will be great bounty #

1579
01:36:22,205 --> 01:36:24,867
“我的上帝…”
# Oh, my God... #

1580
01:36:24,941 --> 01:36:26,875
因为人们仍然需要虾
Since people still needed them shrimps

1581
01:36:26,944 --> 01:36:29,310
来做虾串烧和虾烧烤什么的
for shrimp cocktails and barbecues and all

1582
01:36:29,380 --> 01:36:32,315
而我们的船是唯一剩下的了
and we were the only boat left standing,

1583
01:36:32,383 --> 01:36:34,817
他们只能来布巴甘这里买虾
Bubba Gump shrimp's what they got.

1584
01:36:34,886 --> 01:36:37,821
我们购置了一大堆船
We got a whole bunch of boats.

1585
01:36:37,889 --> 01:36:39,823
有12条珍妮号 还有一个大仓库
12 Jennys, big old warehouse.

1586
01:36:39,892 --> 01:36:41,826
我们还订做了帽子
We even have hats

1587
01:36:41,894 --> 01:36:44,328
上面写着“布巴甘”
that say "Bubba Gump" on them.

1588
01:36:44,397 --> 01:36:45,830
布巴甘捕虾公司
Bubba Gump Shrimp.

1589
01:36:45,899 --> 01:36:47,332
这名字家喻户晓
It's a household name.

1590
01:36:47,401 --> 01:36:49,062
等等 小兄弟
Hold on there, boy.

1591
01:36:49,136 --> 01:36:51,570
你是说你就是…
Are you telling me you're the owner

1592
01:36:51,639 --> 01:36:53,869
布巴捕虾公司的老板？
of the Bubba Gump Shrimp Corporation?

1593
01:36:53,942 --> 01:36:56,877
对 我们挣了一大堆钱
Yes. We got more money than Davy Crockett.

1594
01:36:56,946 --> 01:36:59,881
孩子 我听过很多牛皮
Boy, I heard some whoppers in my time,

1595
01:36:59,949 --> 01:37:02,884
这是最大的一个
but that tops them all.

1596
01:37:04,988 --> 01:37:08,389
我们身边正坐着一个百万富翁
We were sitting next to a millionaire .

1597
01:37:11,395 --> 01:37:16,389
嗯 我觉得那是个很有趣的故事
Well, I thought it was a very lovely story,

1598
01:37:16,468 --> 01:37:19,528
你讲得真好
and you tell it so well,

1599
01:37:19,605 --> 01:37:21,698
非常热情洋溢
with such enthusiasm.

1600
01:37:21,774 --> 01:37:25,870
你想看看丹中尉长什么样吗？
Would you like to see what Lieutenant Dan looks like?

1601
01:37:25,945 --> 01:37:28,175
是的 我想看
Yes, I would.

1602
01:37:32,453 --> 01:37:34,080
这个就是他
That's him right there .

1603
01:37:36,324 --> 01:37:39,384
我再讲点关于丹中尉的事
Let me tell you something about Lieutenant Dan.

1604
01:37:39,462 --> 01:37:40,952
福雷斯…
Forrest...

1605
01:37:46,136 --> 01:37:50,266
我一直还没谢谢你救我一命
I never thanked you for saving my life .

1606
01:38:15,470 --> 01:38:17,904
他从来没说出来
He never actually said so,

1607
01:38:17,973 --> 01:38:22,342
但我想他跟上帝已经讲和了
but I think he made his peace with God.

1608
01:38:29,119 --> 01:38:31,917
这是17天里第二次
For the second time in 17 days,

1609
01:38:31,989 --> 01:38:34,423
福特总幸免被刺杀
President Ford escaped possible assassination today.

1610
01:38:34,492 --> 01:38:37,427
总部呼叫珍妮一号。总部呼叫珍妮一号
Base to Jenny 1. Base to Jenny 1.

1611
01:38:37,495 --> 01:38:38,928
珍妮一号 请说
Jenny 1. Go, Margo.

1612
01:38:38,998 --> 01:38:40,932
有福雷斯的电话
Forrest has a phone call.

1613
01:38:41,000 --> 01:38:45,437
嗯 你跟他说他迟点再回电话
Yeah, well, you'll have to tell them to call him back.

1614
01:38:45,505 --> 01:38:47,939
他现在很忙
He is indisposed at the moment.

1615
01:38:48,008 --> 01:38:49,475
他妈妈病了
His mama's sick.

1616
01:39:08,565 --> 01:39:09,497
妈妈在哪儿？
Where's Mama?

1617
01:39:09,567 --> 01:39:11,364
她在楼上
She's upstairs .

1618
01:39:13,804 --> 01:39:15,533
嗨 福雷斯
Hi, Forrest.

1619
01:39:16,608 --> 01:39:17,802
明天见
I'll see you tomorrow .

1620
01:39:17,876 --> 01:39:19,173
好的
Oh, all right.

1621
01:39:25,551 --> 01:39:28,384
你的腿全好了 是吗 孩子？
Sure got you straightened out, didn't we, boy?

1622
01:39:40,569 --> 01:39:42,059
怎么了 妈妈？
What's the matter, Mama?

1623
01:39:42,138 --> 01:39:45,301
我快死了 福雷斯
I'm dying, Forrest.

1624
01:39:47,444 --> 01:39:50,345
进来 坐下
Come on in, sit down over here .

1625
01:40:04,064 --> 01:40:06,191
为什么你快死了 妈妈？
Why are you dying, Mama?

1626
01:40:06,266 --> 01:40:08,359
我的时候到了
It's my time.

1627
01:40:08,435 --> 01:40:11,495
因为我的时候到了
It's just my time.

1628
01:40:11,572 --> 01:40:13,597
现在…
Oh, now...

1629
01:40:14,675 --> 01:40:17,235
你不用害怕 宝贝
don't you be afraid, sweet heart .

1630
01:40:17,312 --> 01:40:20,713
死亡只是生命的一部分
Death is just a part of life .

1631
01:40:20,782 --> 01:40:24,741
是我们注定要面对的
Something we're all destined to do.

1632
01:40:24,821 --> 01:40:27,153
我并不知道
I didn't know it,

1633
01:40:27,223 --> 01:40:30,158
但我注定要做你的妈妈
but I was destined to be your mama.

1634
01:40:30,227 --> 01:40:32,957
我就尽力做好
I did the best I could.

1635
01:40:33,030 --> 01:40:34,964
你做得很好
You did good.

1636
01:40:35,033 --> 01:40:41,303
嗯…我相信你能实现自己的命运
Well...I happen to believe you make your own destiny .

1637
01:40:41,373 --> 01:40:45,901
你要凭着上帝所给予的做到最好
You have to do the best with what God gave you.

1638
01:40:49,416 --> 01:40:52,010
我的命运是什么 妈妈？
What's my destiny, Mama?

1639
01:40:52,086 --> 01:40:56,523
你要自己去弄明白
You're going to have to figure that out for yourself.

1640
01:40:57,860 --> 01:41:00,795
人生就像一盒各式各样的巧克力
Life is a box of chocolates, Forrest.

1641
01:41:00,863 --> 01:41:03,798
你永远不知道下一块将会是哪种
You never know what you're going to get.

1642
01:41:03,867 --> 01:41:06,802
妈妈总有办法把事情说清楚
Mama always hada way of explaining things

1643
01:41:06,870 --> 01:41:08,804
让我也能听明白
so I could understand them.

1644
01:41:08,872 --> 01:41:10,339
我会想念你的 福雷斯
I will miss you, Forrest.

1645
01:41:12,076 --> 01:41:14,340
她得了癌症
She had got the cancer

1646
01:41:14,411 --> 01:41:16,345
在星期二去世了
and died on a Tuesday.

1647
01:41:16,414 --> 01:41:19,008
我给她买了顶新帽子
I bought her a new hat

1648
01:41:19,084 --> 01:41:21,109
上面有很多小花
with little flowers on it.

1649
01:41:24,056 --> 01:41:26,752
我要说的说是这么多了
And that's all I have to say about that.

1650
01:41:34,035 --> 01:41:36,731
你不是说你在等7路车吗？
Didn't you say you were waiting for the number 7 bus?

1651
01:41:36,804 --> 01:41:39,534
等一下还会有下一班车的
There'll be another one along shortly.

1652
01:41:43,045 --> 01:41:47,482
现在因为我成了足球明星和战争英雄
Now, because I had been a football star and war hero

1653
01:41:47,551 --> 01:41:50,486
以及全国知名的人物和捕虾船的船长
and national celebrity and a shrimping boat captain

1654
01:41:50,554 --> 01:41:51,987
以及大学毕业生
and a college graduate,

1655
01:41:52,056 --> 01:41:54,490
亚拉巴马州绿茵镇的父老乡亲
the city fathers of Greenbow, Alabama,

1656
01:41:54,559 --> 01:41:57,050
决定给我一个好工作
decided to get together and offered me a fine job.

1657
01:41:58,564 --> 01:42:02,091
所以我不再回去和丹中尉一起工作了
So I never went back to work for Lieutenant Dan,

1658
01:42:02,167 --> 01:42:05,102
但他继续打理着我们布巴甘公司的财产
though he did take care of my Bubba Gump money.

1659
01:42:05,171 --> 01:42:08,106
他替我买了一家卖苹果的公司的股票
He got me invested in some kind of fruit company.

1660
01:42:08,174 --> 01:42:10,608
后有他打电话给我
So then I got a call from him

1661
01:42:10,678 --> 01:42:13,238
说我们再也不用担心没钱花了
saying we don't have to worry about money no more,

1662
01:42:13,314 --> 01:42:17,717
我说：“好啊 又少一件麻烦事”
and I said, "That's good. One less thing."

1663
01:42:17,786 --> 01:42:19,583
“我有了新的希望…”
# I've got a new hope... #

1664
01:42:19,654 --> 01:42:22,088
妈妈说过财产不用太多
Now Mama said there's only so much fortune

1665
01:42:22,158 --> 01:42:23,785
一个人用不了多少
a man really needs,

1666
01:42:23,859 --> 01:42:27,260
多余的钱只是用来炫耀
and the rest is just for showing off.

1667
01:42:27,330 --> 01:42:30,231
所以我拿出一大堆
So I gave a whole bunch of it

1668
01:42:30,300 --> 01:42:33,565
给四方福音教堂…
to the Four square Gospel Church...

1669
01:42:33,637 --> 01:42:38,700
又拿出一大堆给拉巴特湾渔场医院…
and I gave a whole bunch to the Bayou La Batre Fishing Hospital...

1670
01:42:40,179 --> 01:42:42,613
虽然布巴已经死了
and even though Bubba was dead

1671
01:42:42,681 --> 01:42:46,117
丹中尉也说我是笨蛋
and Lieutenant Dan said I was nuts,

1672
01:42:46,186 --> 01:42:48,916
我还是把布巴那一份给了布巴的妈妈
I gave Bubba's mama Bubba's share.

1673
01:42:52,293 --> 01:42:53,954
你猜怎么着？
You know what?

1674
01:42:54,028 --> 01:42:57,964
她再也不用去任何人家的厨房干活了
She didn't have to work in nobody's kitchen no more.

1675
01:42:58,032 --> 01:43:00,626
那感觉真不错
That smells wonderful.

1676
01:43:00,702 --> 01:43:03,136
因为我成了亿万富翁
And 'cause I was a gozillionaire

1677
01:43:03,205 --> 01:43:06,140
并且我喜欢干活
and I liked doing it so much,

1678
01:43:06,209 --> 01:43:09,645
我免费帮他们割草
I cut that grass for free.

1679
01:43:11,081 --> 01:43:14,517
但到了晚上无事可干
But at night time when there was nothing to do

1680
01:43:14,585 --> 01:43:17,019
房子空空荡荡的
and the house was all empty,

1681
01:43:17,088 --> 01:43:20,023
我会经常想念珍妮
I'd always think of Jenny.

1682
01:44:23,539 --> 01:44:27,339
然后…她就出现了
And then...she was there.

1683
01:45:00,114 --> 01:45:01,411
